<div class="story"<p>Kitty Dunes heights is a one street cu-de-sac subdivision in Kitty Hawk. There are 29 building lots spread out on either side of Ascension Drive ending at the water front of Kitty Hawk Bay. There is no home owners association and no association fee. You can find Kitty Dunes Heights just past the subdivision of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/kitty-dunes.asp" title="Kitty Dunes">Kitty Dunes</a> as you travel north on Rte 158 and before you get to the community of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/harbour-bay.asp" title="Harbour Bay">Harbour Bay</a>. </p><p><a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/kitty-dunes-heights-covenants.pdf" title="Kitty Dunes Heights restrictive covenants" target="_blank">Kitty Dunes Heights restrictive covenants</a>   - - - <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/Covenant-Disclaimer.asp" target="_blank"><b>    *</b></a></p>
